cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

The paper proposes a novel approach to train deep neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The approach also involves structural optimization of neural networks (cs.AI), which is another sub-category of machine learning. The experimental results also show the effectiveness of the proposed approach in image classification tasks (cs.CV). Finally, the approach is also useful for ensemble classification and progressive inference, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY).
